					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dhanoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4381042); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4381042&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250833" alt="Dhanoj" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4381042)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dhanoj" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4381042); return false;" >Dhanoj</a></span> <span class="odate time_1604200841 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">01 Nov 2020 03:20</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-4808707">
									

<p>Presumably it is the end of everything, and nobody and nothing was left to reboot it. So, essentially everything everywhere in every universe was wiped out, at least thats how im interpreting this. I think its every universe because of the line where they couldnt escape by going to other universes.</p>

