    <div class="post-container" id="fpc-2513599">
                      
		<div class="post" id="post-2513599">
		<div class="long">
			<div class="head">
									<div class="options">
						<a href="javascript:;" onclick="togglePostFold(event,2513599)" class="btn btn-default btn-small btn-sm">Fold</a>
					</div>
								<div class="title" id="post-title-2513599">
																		
															</div>
				<div class="info">
					<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;"  ><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2221240&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610250833" alt="Taffeta" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2221240)"/></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/taffeta" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2221240); return false;" >Taffeta</a></span> <span class="odate time_1464061800 format_%25e%20%25b%20%25Y%2C%20%25H%3A%25M%7Cagohover">24 May 2016 03:50</span>
														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2513599">
									

<p>Aren't endings the point of this canon though? Y'know, first the end of normalcy, then the end of the Foundation, then the end of the other GoIs, and then the end of reality&#8230;</p>
<p>and then the end of this&#8230; entity.</p>
<p>And pizza. And water.</p>

							</div>

								
					
